{"tid":295272,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]有冇巴絲知呢隻咩物種","createTime":"2017-06-23T15:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T06:31:03.000Z","uid":1858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"451747b02da00c9a1b8511060a63d1bc32c13422","tid":295272,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/231202_289c39f1f42dc58997485b97fb24345b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F231202_289c39f1f42dc58997485b97fb24345b.jpg&h=fde43596&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/231204_791d2eb39850688fa2c8f8e2b2c47f03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F231204_791d2eb39850688fa2c8f8e2b2c47f03.jpg&h=7480425f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/231209_fdb4b6b70668c927d831cddca7e024a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F231209_fdb4b6b70668c927d831cddca7e024a6.jpg&h=1dc00473&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起碼第3次見到呢隻野<br />\n<br />\n但係有個奇怪地方，就係次次見到佢都係好似傷左，甚至係冇啦啦死左<br />\n<br />\n上次同今次見到呢隻野都睇落似傷左，佢會飛得好快，碼停咁撞黎撞去，但係過多陣會係啦啦係地下郁得好慢，典下典下咁<br />\n<br />\n有一次仲誇張，朝早起身冇啦啦有一隻死左嘅伏屍係枱面，但係我訓次前完全冇印象見過隻野<br />\n<br />\n依家有d懷疑呢隻野係咪會好似飛蛾撲火咁見到燈光就狗衝，之後辣到傷／死左，但係我除左見到佢地撞牆之外，未試過見到佢地撲燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲知呢隻咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4552252c5659f6a051f6e53fc74960a2e64fbb","tid":295272,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:19:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d56361907aef61299044da5f9eaf138d69a1533","tid":295272,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T15:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75871b2d9374ee496ddc5a9ac906a0e0da366867","tid":295272,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:09:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4a5775262d4686999417ccfee2c0cb914e31f6","tid":295272,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a680af8cab1805a6fb82a7f75593da5a02fdfba","tid":295272,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T06:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}